AN ACT
Relating to the conveyance of certain state property.
Be it enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Missouri, as follows:
1 Section 1. 1. The governor is hereby authorized and
2 empowered to sell, transfer, grant, convey, remise, release,
3 and forever quitclaim all interest of the state of Missouri
4 in property located in Nodaway County, Missouri. The
5 property to be conveyed is more particularly described as
6 follows:
